-Aston-Villa-reaction-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/GeezerButler-Aston-Villa-reaction-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/GeezerButler-Aston-Villa-reaction-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/GeezerButler-Aston-Villa-reaction-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/geezer-butler">吉泽·巴特勒 (Geezer Butler)</a>回应阿斯顿维拉足球俱乐部首次推出全新<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-sabbath">黑色安息日</a>足球装备，称其为“梦想成真”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/ozzy-osbourne-tour-retirement-black-sabbath-3390656">奥兹·奥斯本（Ozzy Osbourne）：无与伦比的摇滚表演者</a></strong></li></ul><p>足球队昨晚（10 月 30 日）在维拉公园对阵水晶宫时首次穿着这件球衣，背面印有金属带的标志性标志。水晶宫以2-1获胜，进入联赛杯四分之一决赛。</p><p> Sabbath 主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ozzy-osbourne">奥兹·奥斯本 (Ozzy Osbourne)</a>和贝斯手巴特勒 (Butler) 都是家乡俱乐部维拉 (Villa) 的忠实粉丝，今年夏天<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-black-sabbath-ozzy-osbourne-geezer-butler-in-aston-villa-kit-trailer-3777109">他们在预告片中推出了球队的新球衣</a>。</p><p>在这段视频中，配乐是“Paranoid”，两人与教练乌奈·埃默里、球员奥利·沃特金斯、埃米利亚诺·马丁内斯和约翰·麦金一起出现。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DBvhNbVttsK/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 